description: Tercen template workflow for the analysis of FlowJo reported statistics and the generation of relevant plots, including ratio heatmaps.
name: Analyzing FlowJo-reported stats

steps.name: Are there any variable names left unmatched?
Are there any samples left unmatched?
Selecting the control per condition (z-score on mean)
Are there any display names used multiple times?
Selecting the control per condition (z-score on median)
Count how many data points per cell
Are there any cells flagged as fail?
Selecting the control per condition (raw median)
Selecting the control per condition (raw mean)

factors.name: exp.value
factors.description: Measurements in long format. The .value output of the Gather step, called exp.value

factors.name: Observation
factors.description: The column from the FlowJo exported file that contains the sample or file names (e.g. samples)

factors.name: sample.Observation
factors.description: The column from the sample annotation file that contains the sample or file names (e.g. sample.samples)

factors.name: sample.Supergroup
factors.description: If the dataset contains data from multiple ELNs, choose sample.ELN. Otherwise, leave blank and click 'Next'.

factors.name: exp.variable
factors.description: FlowJo table columns/headers representing the various sub-populations. The .variable output of the Gather step, called exp.variable

factors.name: cellpop.FlowJo name
factors.description: Column of the display labels file that contains the various FlowJo-reported sub-populations (e.g cellpop.FlowJo name).

factors.name: cellpop.Display name
factors.description: Column of the display labels file that contains the desired labels for the various sub-populations (e.g cellpop.Display name)

factors.name: sample.Group
factors.description: The factor that holds the different compounds or conditions to compare (e.g. sample.compound).
